decks.notes: This deck is focused on generating a large amount of mana quickly and using it to fuel a powerful combo. It utilizes cards like Grim Monolith, Ancient Tomb, Mishra's Workshop, and Moxen to generate mana at an accelerated rate. The combo revolves around Paradoxical Outcome, an instant that returns all nonland permanents you control to your hand, allowing you to draw a card for each one returned. By replaying mana-producing artifacts and generating more mana, the deck aims to continue casting spells and drawing cards until it can assemble a winning board state or combo off for lethal damage.
